            mejora continua.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-center">
            <a href={`mailto:${myEmail}`} class="flex gap-1 b items-center order rounded-lg bg-secondary text-black px-3 h-10 text-center font-semibold cursor-pointer">
